                    />

            <div class="bb-intro-module__card-description">
                We revealed how
                <a href="https://www.propublica.org/article/inside-ziklag-secret-christian-charity-2024-election">Ziklag</a>,
                a secret organization of
                wealthy Christians including the families behind
                Hobby Lobby and Uline, is spending millions to
                try to sway the election and change the country.
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="bb-intro-module__card">
            <div class="bb-intro-module__card-video-container">
                <video muted loop playsinline disablePictureInPicture preload="none" width="216" height="325">
