    <div class="story-card__description">
                
        <h3 class="story-card__hed" >
            <a href="https://www.propublica.org/article/tribal-colleges-universities-federal-funding">
                                    Tribal College Campuses Are Falling Apart. The U.S. Hasn’t Fulfilled Its Promise to Fund the Schools.
                            </a>
        </h3>

        <p class="story-card__dek" >
                            Decades ago, Congress made a commitment to fund a higher education system for Indigenous communities. But a quarter-billion-dollar annual shortfall has led to crimped budgets and crumbling buildings, even as enrollment rises.
                    </p>

        <p class="story-card__byline">
            by <span class="name">Matt Krupnick</span> for <a href="https://www.propublica.org">ProPublica</a>,             <time class="timestamp" datetime="2024-10-14EDT05:00">Oct. 14, 5 a.m. EDT</time>
        </p>

